data.description: Welcome to this charming duplex that has undergone a complete top-to-bottom renovation and offers you a neighborly living experience with great income potential as well. Easily convertible to 2-two bedroom units and nestled in the rapidly developing community of Norris Square, this property features two remarkably spacious one-bedroom units, each with unique features that create warmth, charm and comfort. .  The lower unit boasts an open floor plan and an amazing bathroom complete with a jacuzzi tub, and a cozy rear yard that is just perfect for creating your own personal gardener grilling space. Currently vacant, this unit has estimated rents of $1600/month or more as a two bedroom, making it an ideal investment opportunity to offset the typical mortgage expense for a single family home in this rapidly developing neighborhood.   The upper unit is a bi-level space with an open floor plan that allows natural light to flood the living area, creating an inviting and comfortable atmosphere. The bedroom is exceptionally spacious, and there is even a roof deck opportunity that offers panoramic views of the city skyline. Both units have been thoughtfully upgraded with Brazilian cherry hardwood floors, granite countertops, stunning tile backsplashes, stainless steel appliances, central air, and other essential details that immediately make you feel at home.  The basement is another space that can be leveraged to add even more livable space to the first floor unit. With ample height and square footage, it can easily be finished for an additional bedroom ( additional earning) or other use, providing you with even more flexibility.  Whether you're an investor looking for a cash flow opportunity or an owner-occupant searching for a property in an appreciating area, this is the perfect opportunity for you. Located just minutes away from Norris Square Park, Fishtown, Northern Liberties, and Temple University, this property offers you easy access to all the amenities and attractions that make this neighborhood such a desirable place to live.  With high comps close by suggesting exceptional value with 6 figure rapid equity growth potential, this listing is priced to sell - take the first step towards your dream home or investment property today!
